caption.title: Results of neutralization of dengue 1 and 2 viruses by serum pools without and with depletion of cross-reactive antibodies with Rio Bravo virus E protein.
caption.p: The dotted line indicates the cut-off (c.o.) of the assay. Mean values were calculated from two independent experiments and error bars represent the range. mock dep, mock-depleted serum pool; RB dep, Rio Bravo virus E-depleted serum pool.
